name: T. F. Space Invaders
overview: T. F. Space Invaders is a graphical hack of the original Space Invaders game, as the sprites for the Invaders, the player's(/s') laser cannons, Command Alien Ship, and the bunkers were changed (as the latter are made up of the initials "TF"). Other than the graphical changes, the game plays exactly the same as the original version of the game.
